Step 1:
Install and start beanstalkd

Step 2:
Install pheanstalk 

pear channel-discover pearhub.org
pear install pearhub/Pheanstalk

Step 3:
Edit your ustalk local config, add
	'beanstalk' => array(
		'host' => '127.0.0.1',
		'tube' => 'ustalk'
	)

Step 4:
Add a cronjob which checks that restarts the php job
handler (uStalk/beanstalk_processor.php) every 30 minutes. (PHP eats file handles...)
